%% Trace: features/05-App生物辨識啟用.feature
sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant App as AppMobile
    participant OS as DeviceBiometricAPI
    participant Ctrl as BiometricController
    participant Svc as BiometricEnrollmentService
    participant Auth as JwtAuthGuard
    participant Repo as BiometricDeviceTokenRepository
    participant DB as PostgreSQL

    Note over User,App: 使用者已以密碼/OTP 登入，持有 session token
    User->>App: 帳號設定 → 啟用生物辨識
    App->>OS: 觸發 Face ID / Touch ID / 指紋
    OS-->>App: 通過 (本人確認)
    App->>Ctrl: POST /biometric/enable (device_id, platform) [Authorization: Bearer]
    Ctrl->>Auth: validateJwt(bearer)
    Auth-->>Ctrl: currentUserId
    Ctrl->>Svc: enable(member_auth_id=currentUserId, device_id, platform)
    Svc->>Svc: generateRefreshToken()
    Svc->>Repo: upsert BiometricDeviceToken(member_auth_id, device_id, platform, refresh_token_hash)
    Repo->>DB: INSERT/UPDATE biometric_device_tokens
    Svc-->>Ctrl: refresh_token (raw)
    Ctrl-->>App: 201 {refresh_token}
    App->>OS: 加密儲存於 Keychain / Keystore (BR-59)
    OS-->>App: stored
    App-->>User: 已啟用生物辨識
